manager = GroupManager(Name('Alice'), Name('data_type'),
    Sqlite3GroupManagerDb(self.eKeyDatabaseFilePath), 1024, 1, self.keyChain)
self.setManager(manager)
data = manager._createEKeyData('20150825T090000', '20150825T110000', self.
    encryptKeyBlob)
self.assertEqual('/Alice/READ/data_type/E-KEY/20150825T090000/20150825T110000',
    data.getName().toUri())
contentBlob = data.getContent()
self.assertTrue(self.encryptKeyBlob.equals(contentBlob))
